[{"type":"warning","header":"","html":"<p><code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">session-id</code> 必须至少 33 个字符。上述命令会自动生成足够长度的 ID。<code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">--stream</code> 启用实时输出显示。</p>"},{"type":"info","header":"我都带了 --actor-id 了,它怎么还问我是谁?","html":"<p>这是预期的,别奇怪。<code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">--actor-id</code> / <code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">--user-id</code> <strong>不是\"告诉 Agent 你是谁\",它只是 Memory(记忆)的分区钥匙</strong>——后台用它决定\"这次对话的记忆存进哪个抽屉、从哪个抽屉读\",模型本身并看不到这个值,更不会自动把它解析成一份员工档案(姓名、工龄、部门)。</p><p>所以当你问\"我有多少天假期\",会遇到两件事叠加:</p><ol>\n<li><strong>这是第一次对话,这个抽屉是空的</strong>——Memory 里还没存过这个 actor 的任何偏好/事实,即使 actor-id 给了也没东西可读。</li>\n<li><strong>查个人余额需要具体工号</strong>——<code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">check_leave_balance</code> 这类工具要一个明确的员工 ID 才能查,而 actor-id 没作为身份喂给模型,所以它只能反过来问你要。</li>\n</ol><p>区分两种\"知道\":<strong>政策怎么写的</strong>来自知识库(所以年假政策那段它答得出);<strong>你是谁、你的余额</strong>要靠 Memory 累积或带 ID 查工具,这两样第一次对话时都还没有。等后面 Memory 攒了几轮,个性化才会显现——这恰恰是本页\"裸表现基线\"想让你看到的。</p>"},{"type":"error","header":"Unknown directive","html":""},{"type":"warning","header":"","html":"<p>如果 Agent 返回错误（例如 \"Tool execution failed\"），请检查 Gateway 是否已部署完成：<code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">aws bedrock-agentcore-control list-gateways --region us-west-2 --query \"items[?name==\\</code>hrgateway`].status\"<code data-inline=\"true\" class=\"awsui_root_18wu0_o6mtu_939 awsui_box_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_code-variant_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_color-default_18wu0_o6mtu_172 awsui_font-size-default_18wu0_o6mtu_188 awsui_font-weight-default_18wu0_o6mtu_229\">，应为 </code>READY`。</p>"},{"type":"success","header":"","html":"<p>你已经拿到了\"优化前\"的基线快照。记住这次回答——Phase 4 会用评估器给它打分、诊断问题,Phase 5 改完之后再用同样的问题对比,看分数有没有真的变好。</p>"}]